45
00:05:31,650 --> 00:05:32,730
It bothers you ?

46
00:05:32,730 --> 00:05:33,550
Yeah.

47
00:05:34,250 --> 00:05:38,040
I just thought, "Until recently, you
couldn't even reach the strap handle."

48
00:05:38,640 --> 00:05:40,900
Oh, that ?

49
00:05:40,900 --> 00:05:42,100
Didn't I tell you ?

50
