When I'm needed by someone...

55
00:06:42,100 --> 00:06:48,950
...I learn for the first time where I am right now.

56
00:06:48,950 --> 00:06:56,600
Just as the metronome gets interrupted...

57
00:06:56,600 --> 00:07:04,560
...so few people can hear the monotonous sound.

58
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:12,480
With a clunk, I place my forehead on the display window.

59
00:07:12,480 --> 00:07:22,030
For what can I cry ? I look up beyond the sky.

60
00:07:22,030 --> 00:07:29,840
When you're not with me, you overflow.

61
00:07:29,840 --> 00:07:38,030
On the streets and by the windows, the clues overflow.

62
00:07:38,030 --> 00:07:46,310
Loneliness doesn't corner us.

63
00:07:46,310 --> 00:07:54,530
